Frequently Asked Questions

How do I register as a buyer or supplier?

Registration is simple! Click on the "Register" button in the header, choose your role (buyer or supplier), and follow the step-by-step process. You'll need to provide basic business information and verify your email and phone number.

What are the fees for using MarsaFyi?

Registration is completely free for both buyers and suppliers. We charge a small commission only on successful transactions, which is clearly communicated before any purchase is made.

How do you ensure product quality and supplier reliability?

All suppliers go through a rigorous verification process including document verification, business registration checks, and sample product testing. We also maintain a comprehensive rating and review system based on real transactions.

What payment methods do you support?

We support multiple payment methods including credit/debit cards, bank transfers, and digital wallets. For international transactions, we also offer secure escrow services to protect both buyers and sellers.
